name: Warren Digger
summary: You've learned to put your sturdy claws to work digging through the earth.
description:
You've learned to put your sturdy claws to work digging through the earth. You gain a burrow Speed of 15 feet.Traits

Ratfolk: A creature with this trait is a member of the ratfolk ancestry. Ratfolk are humanoids who resemble rats. An ability with this trait can be used or selected only by ratfolk.
